snippet.title: Happy Birthday, Oliver! First Birthday Party with Diana and Roma
snippet.description:
Baby Oliver is 1 year old! We celebrated his First Birthday together with the whole big family! Diana, Roma and all the guests congratulate the baby and give him many gifts and toys! Children and adults have fun and play together. Happy First Birthday, Oliver!
Thanks for watching!
